{"word":"ὑποκάτω","slug":"ὑποκάτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὑποϰάτω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὑπό\">ὑπό</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κάτω\">κάτω</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> functioning in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> only as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prep.\">prep.</a> indicating a position that is ‘at a lower level than’, <b>under, beneath<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on spatial position as such <b><a href='B:480 7:28'>Mk 7:28</a>; <a href='B:490 8:16'>Lk 8:16</a>; <a href='B:500 1:50'>J 1:50</a>; <a href='B:730 6:9'>Rv 6:9</a>;</b> in related vein, of position under a surface <b><a href='B:480 6:11'>Mk 6:11</a>; <a href='B:730 5:3'>Rv 5:3</a>, <a href='B:730 5:13'>13</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> component of subjection <b><a href='B:470 22:44'>Mt 22:44</a>; <a href='B:480 12:36'>Mk 12:36</a>; <a href='B:650 2:8'>Hb 2:8</a>; <a href='B:730 12:1'>Rv 12:1</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑποζώννυμι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑπόκειμαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}